Merchants Bank Isn’t Aware of Buffett Investment Plan

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-03-03T09:24:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-03/china-merchants-bank-s-ma-not-aware-of-buffett-investment-plan.html
China  Merchants Bank  Co., the
nation’s sixth-largest lender, isn’t aware of any plan by
billionaire  Warren Buffett  to invest in the company, President
Ma Weihua said in Beijing in response to a reporter’s question.  Buffett may buy shares of Shenzhen-based Merchants Bank  in  Hong Kong , the National Business Daily  reported  today, citing an
unidentified blog on sina.com.  Shares of Merchants Bank surged 4.2 percent to close at
14.03 yuan in Shanghai and gained 2.3 percent to HK$19.76 in
Hong Kong.  To contact the reporter on this story:  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
